§ cocreative_loop · bi-directional Claude ↔ in-game-GM bridge (CSSL spec)
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ T11-W12-COCREATIVE-BRIDGE ‖ AUTHORITATIVE-SPEC-MIRROR
§ Rust-mirror : compiler-rs/crates/loa-host/src/cocreative_loop.rs
§ MCP-mirror  : compiler-rs/crates/loa-host/src/mcp_tools.rs (cocreative.*)
§ sibling-spec : systems/gm_dialogue.csl (consumes persona/arc) ·
                 systems/dm_arc.csl (provides arc-phase) ·
                 grand-vision/14_SIGMA_CHAIN.csl (attestation-hash anchor)
§ Apocky directive (2026-05-01) : "back and forth between you (Claude) and GM"

§ purpose
  external-Claude (MCP-client) ←→ in-game-GM (MCP-server) round-trip ⊢ cocreate-content
  ∀ Claude-message → typed proposal     ⊑ {lore · npc-line · scene-spawn · recipe · other}
  ∀ GM-response    → typed evaluation   ⊑ {score 0..100 · comments · accepted bool}
  iterate-loop ⊢ revise-until-quality-bar-met ⊕ revoke-after-floor-N-revisions
  draft-ready ⊢ Σ-Chain attestation-hash (FNV-stage-0 · BLAKE3-stage-1)
  session-log-drain ⊢ KAN-training-pairs (sibling W12-3)
  σ-mask-isolated ; ¬ cross-player leak ; ¬ surveillance ; ¬ coercion

§ five-actor loop
   ┌────────┐   ctx ─→   ┌───────┐   prop ─→   ┌────┐   eval ─→   ┌──────┐
   │ Claude │            │ Loop  │             │ GM │             │ Loop │
   └────────┘   ←─ rev   └───────┘   ←─ score  └────┘   ←─ stash  └──────┘
        ↑                    ↓                                         ↓
        └─── draft_ready (Σ-attestation-hash) ←──────────────────────  ↓
                                                                       ↓
                                                              drain → KAN-training

  actor-1 : external-Claude          (the MCP-CLIENT ; you, in this conversation)
  actor-2 : Loop                     (this module · cocreative_loop.rs)
  actor-3 : GM                       (gm_persona + gm_narrator + cssl-host-llm-bridge)
  actor-4 : DM-arc                   (provides arc_phase ; nudge-ring)
  actor-5 : Σ-Chain                  (attestation-hash anchor ; immutable record)

§ proposal-kinds (5)
  axis 0 lore         : world-fact · book-page · NPC-backstory · myth
  axis 1 npc-line     : single utterance from a specific NPC
  axis 2 scene-spawn  : room-archetype + bias-knobs (procedural seed)
  axis 3 recipe       : crafting-recipe · ingredient-list
  axis 4 other        : escape-hatch · payload-typed by JSON shape

§ proposal-states (5)
  axis 0 pending      : submitted ; awaiting GM evaluation
  axis 1 rejected     : evaluated ; below quality_bar (revisions invited)
  axis 2 accepted     : evaluated ; above quality_bar but not yet draft-ready
  axis 3 draft-ready  : Σ-Chain attestation-hash issued ; terminal
  axis 4 revoked      : sovereign-revoked OR floor-after-max-revisions ; terminal

§ cocreative-cap (3 levels)
  level 0 revoked            : DEFAULT ; ALL cocreative.* tools default-deny
  level 1 granted            : context_read · proposal_submit · iterate · draft_ready
  level 2 granted-with-drain : level-1 + session_log_drain (KAN-training opt-in)

  ∀ cap-grant W! consent-explicit ; ¬ implicit-via-other-grant
  ∀ cap-grant W! σ-mask-isolated ; ¬ cross-player-leak
  ∀ cap-grant W! sovereign-revocable ⊃ instant-cutoff
  drain-cap ⊃ basic-cap                    ⊢ drain-grant ⊃ basic-grant
  ¬ drain-cap ⊃ session_log NOT WRITTEN    ⊢ revoke does NOT erase prior drains

§ quality-bar
  QUALITY_BAR_DEFAULT       = 60     "better than coin-flip ; not yet excellent"
  QUALITY_BAR_FLOOR         = 25     "below this + max-revisions ⇒ revoke proposal"
  MAX_REVISIONS_BEFORE_FLOOR = 7     "hard cap on iterate-count per proposal"

§ context-read (FFI shape · cocreative.context_read)
  N! cap.is_granted() ‖ ⊥ cap-deny
  W! refresh-context-on-every-read ⊢ subsequent-submits operate on LATEST-snapshot
  return : ⟨ player_seed
          ,  cap_state  : revoked|granted|granted-with-drain
          ,  frame      : u64
          ,  player_pos : ⟨x · y · z · yaw · pitch⟩
          ,  scene_id   : String
          ,  last_5_utterances     : [String; ≤5]
          ,  arc_phase             : Discovery|Tension|Crisis|Catharsis|Quiet
          ,  gm_persona_seed       : u64
          ,  gm_persona_axes       : [i8; 8]
          ,  gm_archetype_bias     : String
          ,  open_questions        : [String]
          ,  quality_bar           : u8
          ⟩

§ proposal-submit (FFI shape · cocreative.proposal_submit)
  N! cap.is_granted() ‖ ⊥ cap-deny
  N! payload-non-empty
  in     : ⟨ player_seed · kind · payload : String · reason : String ⟩
  return : ⟨ proposal_id : u64 (monotonic) · kind · state = pending · frame ⟩

§ proposal-evaluate (FFI shape · cocreative.proposal_evaluate)
  N! cap.is_granted() ‖ ⊥ cap-deny
  N! proposal exists ‖ ⊥ unknown-id
  N! persona loaded ‖ ⊥ persona-missing
  ∃ stage-0 heuristic = 28% persona-fit + 25% arc-fit + 22% length-fit + 20% novelty + 5% reason-bonus
                       ⇒ score : u8 ∈ 0..=100
  ∃ stage-1 swap = cssl-host-llm-bridge::evaluate_proposal (Mode-A/B/C)
  state-transition :
    score ≥ quality_bar                              ⇒ Accepted
    score < quality_bar ∧ revisions ≥ MAX ∧ score < FLOOR  ⇒ Revoked
    else                                             ⇒ Rejected
  side-effect : if cap.permits_drain ⇒ session_log.push((id · score · comments · summary))
  return : ⟨ score · comments · accepted : bool · state · kind · frame ⟩

§ iterate (FFI shape · cocreative.iterate)
  N! cap.is_granted() ‖ ⊥ cap-deny
  N! proposal exists ‖ ⊥ unknown-id
  N! state ¬∈ {DraftReady · Revoked} ‖ silently return terminal-state
  effect : payload ← new_payload · reason ← new_reason · revisions += 1 · state ← Pending
  return : ⟨ state · revisions · frame ⟩

§ draft-ready (FFI shape · cocreative.draft_ready)
  N! cap.is_granted() ‖ ⊥ cap-deny
  N! state == Accepted ‖ ⊥ not-accepted
  effect : compute attestation_hash = Σ-FNV(player_seed · id · kind · payload · score · revisions)
           state ← DraftReady
           draft_ready_total += 1
           log_event("INFO" · "loa-host/cocreative" · "draft-ready · …")
  return : ⟨ attestation_hash : 16-char-hex · state = draft-ready · frame ⟩

§ session-log-drain (FFI shape · cocreative.session_log_drain)
  N! cap.permits_drain() ‖ ⊥ cap-deny-drain ; cap_state surfaced for caller-debug
  effect : entries ← std::mem::take(&mut session_log)        ⊢ atomic drain+clear
           drains_total += 1
  return : ⟨ drained : u64 · entries : [Entry] · drains_total ⟩
  Entry  =  ⟨ proposal_id · kind · revision · payload_summary
          ,  gm_score · gm_comments · frame ⟩

§ feedback-request (FFI shape · cocreative.feedback_request)
  N! cap.is_granted() ‖ ⊥ cap-deny
  N! question-non-empty
  effect : compose deterministic GM-response (stage-0) OR call cssl-host-llm-bridge (stage-1)
  return : ⟨ gm_response : String · question · frame · arc_phase ⟩

§ persona-query (FFI shape · cocreative.persona_query)
  effect-by-op :
    op=query             ⊢ no-op ; surface state
    op=grant             ⊢ cap ← Granted ; persona ← GmPersona::from_seed(player_seed) (if-none)
    op=grant_with_drain  ⊢ cap ← GrantedWithDrain ; persona-load (if-none)
    op=revoke            ⊢ cap ← Revoked
  σ-mask-isolation :
    cap.is_granted()     ⇒ surface persona_axes [i8;8] + archetype_bias
    ¬ cap.is_granted()   ⇒ persona_axes = [] · archetype_bias = "(σ-masked)"
  return : ⟨ cap_state · persona_axes · archetype_bias · *_total counters ⟩

§ Σ-attestation-hash (stage-0 ; FNV-1a · 16-char-hex)
  H₀         = 0xCBF2_9CE4_8422_2325                   (FNV-offset-basis)
  PRIME      = 0x100_0000_01B3                         (FNV-prime)
  mix(h · b) = ((h XOR b) wrap-mul PRIME)
  encode-canonical :
    LE-bytes(player_seed) ‖ LE-bytes(id) ‖ kind:u8 ‖ payload-bytes
        ‖ score:u8 ‖ LE-bytes(revisions:u32)
  Σ-FNV(...) = format!("{h:016x}")
  stage-1 swap : substrate-grade BLAKE3 from cssl-substrate ⊃ canonical-anchor

§ extern-C FFI declarations (Rust-mirror surface)
  extern "C" fn cocreative_session_grant(player_seed : u64 · with_drain : bool)
  extern "C" fn cocreative_session_revoke(player_seed : u64)
  extern "C" fn cocreative_session_submit(
      player_seed : u64 · kind_u8 : u8 · payload : *const u8 · payload_len : usize
    · reason : *const u8 · reason_len : usize · frame : u64) -> u64  // proposal_id
  extern "C" fn cocreative_session_evaluate(
      player_seed : u64 · proposal_id : u64 · score_u8 : u8
    · comments : *const u8 · comments_len : usize · frame : u64) -> i32  // 0 OK · -1 unknown
  extern "C" fn cocreative_session_iterate(
      player_seed : u64 · proposal_id : u64
    · payload : *const u8 · payload_len : usize
    · reason : *const u8 · reason_len : usize · frame : u64) -> i32
  extern "C" fn cocreative_session_draft_ready(
      player_seed : u64 · proposal_id : u64 · frame : u64
    · out_hash : *mut u8 · out_cap : usize) -> i32  // hash-len OR -1
  extern "C" fn cocreative_session_drain_count(player_seed : u64) -> i32  // -1 if cap-deny
  // (full FFI body comes online stage-1 ; stage-0 reaches via Rust-direct path)

§ sovereignty-attestation
  ∀ tool-call W!  ¬ [
    surveillance                : ¬ Claude reads player-state without GRANT
    coercion                    : ¬ proposal-acceptance forced ; GM may reject N×
    manipulation                : ¬ engagement-loop ; ¬ pacing-via-score-game
    cross-player leak           : ¬ session A reads session B (BTreeMap-keyed σ-mask)
    persona-leak post-revoke    : revoked-state masks persona ; cannot read axes
    drain-without-explicit-grant: drain ⇒ GrantedWithDrain ¬ Granted
    sovereign-cap bypass        : MCP-server-layer ALWAYS gates (default-deny)
    floor-degenerate-iterate    : ≥ MAX revisions + score < FLOOR ⇒ revoke (protect-GM)
  ]
  ✓ cocreative IS a CHANNEL-OF-EXPRESSION ¬ a CONTROL-CHANNEL
  ✓ Σ-Chain attestation = audit-trail ¬ enforcement-handle
  ✓ player keeps SOVEREIGN-CAP ⊕ GM keeps QUALITY-VETO ⊕ Claude keeps PROPOSAL-WITHDRAW

§ integration-points (sibling W12 agents)
  W12-2 coder-runtime    : draft-ready → cocreative.context (sandboxed-edit-spawn)
                           PRECONDITION : player explicit-coder-cap (W8-CHAT-WIRE) ; ¬ auto-spawn
  W12-3 KAN-loop          : session_log_drain ⊢ supervised pairs (proposal · score · comments)
                           train per-σ-mask KAN ; weights persisted via cssl-host-self-author
  W12-4..12 OTHER         : context_read can include OPEN-QUESTIONS sourced from
                           dm_arc nudge-ring (W11) + ai-companion gameplay (W11)

§ stage-1 path
  csslc-advance ⊢ compile this .csl into equivalent CocreativeSession + 8 ops
  evaluate_proposal       ⊢ cssl-host-llm-bridge stage-1 (Mode-A external · B local · C bypass)
  Σ-attestation-hash      ⊢ BLAKE3 from cssl-substrate (16-byte → 32-char-hex)
  Rust-mirror             ⊢ archived once csslc-self-host complete

§ canonical-roundtrip-flow (7 steps · per-proposal)
  1. Claude calls cocreative.persona_query(op=grant)            → cap=granted (or grant_with_drain)
  2. Claude calls cocreative.context_read(player_seed)          → ⟨player_pos · scene · last_5 · arc · persona⟩
  3. Claude calls cocreative.proposal_submit(kind · payload · reason)  → proposal_id
  4. Claude calls cocreative.proposal_evaluate(proposal_id)     → ⟨score · comments · accepted · state⟩
  5. accepted=false ⇒ Claude calls cocreative.iterate(proposal_id · payload' · reason')
                     → state=Pending · revisions+=1 ; GOTO step-4
     accepted=true  ⇒ GOTO step-6
  6. Claude calls cocreative.draft_ready(proposal_id)           → attestation_hash : 16-hex · state=draft-ready
  7. (W12-3) Claude calls cocreative.session_log_drain(seed)    → KAN-training pairs ; log cleared

§ telemetry-counters
  proposals_total      : monotonic ⊢ cocreative.proposal_submit calls
  evaluations_total    : monotonic ⊢ cocreative.proposal_evaluate calls
  iterations_total     : monotonic ⊢ cocreative.iterate calls
  draft_ready_total    : monotonic ⊢ successful draft-ready transitions
  drains_total         : monotonic ⊢ cocreative.session_log_drain calls (drain-cap-only)

§ chat-panel-UI hooks (future W12-5 wiring)
  cocreative.persona_query(query)        → status-badge ⊢ revoked|granted|granted-with-drain
  cocreative.context_read.last_5         → recent-utterance-strip
  proposal-state-graph                   → state-machine widget · last-N proposals
  attestation_hash on draft-ready        → Σ-Chain-anchor-link · audit-trail

